:: A Doorway on Dean Street {"position":"700,550","size":"100,100"}
(set: $hadBreather to true)
(set: $confidence to $confidence + 15)

You're flagging now; you're almost west.

Stand here to catch your breath and gather your thoughts.

(if: $hadPhoneCall is true)[You close your eyes and see them: Aoifein the dark flat, the baby wrapped in whatever she could find. You can't stop now.]

[[Continue|Dean Street]]


