You are on the floor. The cellar ceiling rotates slowly above you, like a thought you cannot complete. Copper stands over you, barely winded; he could do this all night and you both know it.

'Brave,' he says. 'Stupid, but brave.'

[[Try to get up|Beaten]]


:: Fight R1 Back {"position":"2100,750","size":"100,100"}
<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-lose">CAUGHT</span></div>
</div>

You step back but the wall has other ideas; it meets you like an old debt. Copper's fist finds your shoulder and spins you like a thought he's having about you.

'No room down here,' he says. 'Did nobody mention?'

[[Round 2|Fight Round 2]]


:: Fight R1 Block {"position":"2000,750","size":"100,100"}
(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 1)

<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score">ABSORBED</div>
</div>

You get your arms up. The impact travels through your bones like news through a small town: everyone knows at once.

You are still standing. This surprises you both.

'You can take one,' says Copper. 'Good. There's more where that came from.'

[[Round 2|Fight Round 2]]


:: Fight R1 Duck {"position":"1900,750","size":"100,100"}
(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 2)

<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-win">CLEAN</span></div>
</div>

You fold beneath it. His knuckles whistle through the space where your skull had been, where it is not, where it will never be again.

For a breath he is off-balance; in his eyes you see a question form.

'Quick,' he admits. 'Let's see about lucky.'

[[Round 2|Fight Round 2]]


:: Fight R2 Catch {"position":"2000,950","size":"100,100"}
(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 1)

<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score">ABSORBED</div>
</div>

You catch his wrist. For a moment you are locked together, breathing each other's air, intimate as lovers or as enemies; in Soho these are often the same.

He wrenches free. The jab dies undelivered.

'Interesting,' he says. 'Most writers don't fight back.'

[[Round 3|Fight Round 3]]


:: Fight R2 Counter {"position":"2100,950","size":"100,100"}
(set: _counterChance to (random: 1, 10))
(if: _counterChance >= 6)[(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 3)

<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-win">★ COUNTER ★</span></div>
</div>

You let the jab come. It rocks your head back; stars bloom behind your eyes like flowers in a cemetery. But your own fist is already travelling, and it finds the soft country beneath his ribs.

Copper folds. The sound he makes is not language.

'Bastard,' he gasps, when he can. But his eyes are smiling.

[[Round 3|Fight Round 3]]]
(else:)[<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-lose">CAUGHT</span></div>
</div>

You try to counter but your body is slower than your ambition. His jab snaps your head back. Blood in your mouth, copper-bright. The cellar swims like something seen through bathwater.

'Don't get clever,' says Copper. 'Clever gets you dead.'

[[Round 3|Fight Round 3]]]


:: Fight R2 Slip {"position":"1900,950","size":"100,100"}
(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 2)

<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-win">CLEAN</span></div>
</div>

You slip sideways; his knuckles graze your cheek like a rumour, like something that nearly happened but didn't.

He grunts. Annoyance or respect; the Maltese don't differentiate.

'Slippery,' he says. 'Like a poet.'

[[Round 3|Fight Round 3]]


:: Fight R3 Clinch {"position":"2000,1150","size":"100,100"}
(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 1)

You step inside his reach and clinch him. His uppercut has nowhere to go; it dies against your shoulder. You are chest to chest now, breathing hard, close as dancers, close as grief.

